---
import Card from "./Card/index.astro";
---

<Card colSpan="md:col-span-1" rowSpan="md:row-span-7" title="About me">
  <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
    <div class="text-sm font-light">
      <p>
        Hi, I'm Achraf Ouazzani Chahdi, a Cybersecurity Specialist and a Software Engineer.
        <br />
        My primary Skills are:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside">
        <li>Penetration Testing</li>
        <li>Web Application Security</li>
        <li>Network Security</li>
        <li>Incident Response</li>
        <li>Web Development</li>
        <li>Manual and Automated Testing</li>
        
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="text-sm font-light">
      <p>
        I have experience with a wide range of technologies, including:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside">
        <li>Python</li>
        <li>JavaScript</li>
        <li>SQL</li>
        <li>NoSQL</li>
        <li>Git</li>
        <li>Linux</li>
        <li>Bash</li>
        <li>and many more...</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <p class="text-sm font-light">
      While I have some preferred tools, I always choose the best one for the
      job, even if it's not on my usual list. My goal is to find the right
      solution for each problem.
    </p>
  </div>
</Card>
